headline: Teradyne Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., January 26, 2026--Teradyne, Inc. (NASDAQ:TER) today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.12 per share, payable on March 13, 2026, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on February 13, 2026.
